{"tid":1762953,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際戰線幫幫手】一 人 一 抗 爭 歌","createTime":"2019-11-30T03:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T17:36:56.000Z","uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbfac661562fa55087d59d1c055576e34fc9bf6","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:21:21.000Z","msg":"沉咗再 po 過，幫手推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">是咁的，有外國朋友想整一個網頁，<span style=\"color: red;\">每個月以一個抗爭地方做主題整 playlist，收集同記錄世界各地唔同抗爭者喺社運時期聽嘅歌，原因喺想以音樂 connect 大家 ，以唔同方法保留大家抗爭時嘅感覺同埋經歷</span>，同時分享世界唔同角落嘅抗爭消息。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港會係第一個 playlist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>，之後會繼續收集嚟自智利，伊拉克，加泰隆尼亞等等地方嘅歌。遲少少可能會開一個 physical location 喺法國 Normandy 一個叫做 Caen 嘅城市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想要咩歌：<br />\n可以係代表到運動嘅歌曲 / 自家製 / 任何喺運動期間觸動到自己嘅音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">樓主就幫大家寫咗《榮光》先，大家自由發揮，鐘意嘅都可以分享下聽歌感受，或者點解揀呢啲歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者大家有咩 creative input 都可以發表下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n朋友 message 原文：<br />\n<br />\nThe &laquo; Cobbles of Caen &raquo; / Le pav&eacute; Caennais<br />\n<br />\nI am writing you about a French project I&rsquo;m involved in, a local news website which aims to inform the public about local struggle actions. I&rsquo;m undertaking the &laquo; cultural page &raquo;. The project has just started and the website is still under-construction. The idea is to publish, every month a music playlist made by a collective in struggle, a good way to bring people to it. As the Yellow Jacket in France is now finding new ways to mobilize people, we need to adapt and share our struggles. <br />\n<br />\nHK is engaged in a fight against CPC since several months, we support you and would like to inform others about your cause. Behind the singularities of national actions, music is keen to gather people.<br />\n<br />\nThe playlist we are working on is wildly open and I would like to integrate songs of the HK protest. So what do you listen to recently ? It can be a protest song, HK pop or even mainstream music.<br />\n<br />\nThanks for your attention. And don&rsquo;t give up the fight !<br />\n<br />\nAll the best!"},{"pid":"a83f10e94cc08cf664fcc1f540be5fd401561ede","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3094000929f76df79a791dbfa6353021b88122d3","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1222889e0af16496d5426f11b0eb20968a6c91e6","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212875e449bf0a14a39490bfda07e6d3cbf0f48d","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd346f2043122dd208a0b45c592335655999eeba","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42428a471a34f377a22c1ef5ea9d84583b41ac1","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164ce8251576dc20320355bdd3ef2a154575fa0c","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8dd71b4941078693b42e062f9c00b0e2df5658","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc7975e0a098619314bd8f84480fb6d2897640d","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9268e4bfe8af0130e0dae1ad309cbebdc149e6a","tid":1762953,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d08f67a51893a2023b7072ef231b7da0cbd073d","tid":1762953,"uid":73804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T17:24:40.000Z","msg":"可以加Bauhinia Rhapsody"},{"pid":"10083fac8866f93ec7b66ebfa1daeb816b132de3","tid":1762953,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T17:25:03.000Z","msg":"我估主要都係呢兩首"},{"pid":"3805845eae7287faf996f973a04a9262ade39713","tid":1762953,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"不屈進行曲<br />\n和你飛<br />\nfuck the popo"},{"